                  <summary><p>The <title xml:lang="sa">Karuṇāvajrāyudha</title> is a 13<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>-century drama by the Jain monk <persName xml:lang="sa">Bālacandra</persName>. It elaborates upon the story of the <term xml:lang="sa">śyenakapotīya</term>, the hawk and the dove. This text was edited by <persName xml:lang="sa">Muni Caturavijayaji</persName> in 1916.</p>
